      "span_text": "The monomer (2-(2,5-di(thiophen-2-yl) thiophen-3-yl) acetic acid), an acetic acid functionalized-terthiophene molecule referred to as 3-TAA, has been synthesized in our group using a previously reported procedure [CITATION_1] .",
